object (SponsoredProductsReducedObjectIdFilter)
Filter entities by the list of objectIds

includeExtendedDataFields	
boolean
Whether to get entity with extended data fields such as creationDate, lastUpdateDate, servingStatus

locale	
string
Restricts results to negativeKeywords that match the specified locale.

matchTypeFilter	
Array of strings (SponsoredProductsNegativeMatchType)
Items Enum: "NEGATIVE_BROAD" "NEGATIVE_EXACT" "NEGATIVE_PHRASE" "OTHER"
Only the negativeKeyword with the match type that is in this list will be listed

maxResults	
integer <int32>
Number of records to include in the paginated response. Defaults to max page size for given API

negativeKeywordIdFilter	
object (SponsoredProductsObjectIdFilter)
Filter entities by the list of objectIds

negativeKeywordTextFilter	
object (SponsoredProductsKeywordTextFilter)
Filter by keywordText

nextToken	
string
token value allowing to navigate to the next response page

stateFilter	
object (SponsoredProductsEntityStateFilter)
Filter entities by state. To filter live entities, only 'ENABLED', 'PAUSED' and 'ARCHIVED' can be used

